---
title: BBQ Plant-Based Ground Protein Meatballs with Smashed Potatoes and Garlicky Broccoli
description: These tasty meatballs are flavoured with BBQ spices and garlic, sweetened with a sprinkling of chives, then tossed in a tangy BBQ sauce. This comfort food classic satisfies on any night of the week!
